blockword.embedDes: This feature allows you to block words.
blockword.embedField2: If you need help check out our [configuration guide](https://docs.discordsafe.com/docs/config/blockedwords) or ask on our [support server](https://discordsafe.com/discord).
blockword.embedField4:
`blockword add` - Add one or more words.
`blockword remove` - Remove one or more words.
`blockword add pack` - Blocks a group of pre-selected words.
`blockword remove pack` - Unlocks a group of pre-selected words.
`blockword list` - Shows the list of blocked words on the server.
`blockword reset` - Removes all words.
blockword.embedRDescription:
**This action is irreversible.
Are you sure? You have 30 seconds.
Answer with **yes**.

blockword.packsDescription:
Blocked word packs save time and directly block the most common offensive words.

- **Block a pack with:** `{prefix}}{{commandName}} add pack <Number>`
- **Unlock a pack with:** `{prefix}}{{commandName}} remove pack <Number>`.
blockword.packsField2:
`0` - Recommended words, slightly offensive.
`1` - Offensive words and insults.
`2` - Inappropriate and explicit words.

help.descripci√≥n:
Hi, I'm **D-Safe**, a bot dedicated to moderation, utility and security, created to solve all your server problems.

I've been **{{tiempo}}** online helping **{{servidores}}** servers with **{{comandos}}** commands.
My prefix on this server is `{{prefix}}`, to see my commands use `{{prefix}}commands`.
help.embedFeature1d: We have launched a new update with a lot of improvements. [Change Log](https://blog.discordsafe.com/)
help.embedFeature2d: [Vote me for support](https://top.gg/bot/461171501715161108/vote) while you get improvements with [D-Safe Premium](https://discordsafe.com/premium), check out our [Discord server](https://discordsafe.com/discord).
help.embedFeature3d: Help us to improve and maintain the translation of the bot in other languages, [ask in the support server](https://discordsafe.com/invite).
help.embedFeature4d: If you find a bad translation, please report it to [the support server](https://discordsafe.com/discord).
help.embedSuggestion2: You can ban multiple users with `{{prefix}}hackban`.
help.embedSuggestion3: You can set my prefix with`{{prefix}}setprefix`.
help.embedSuggestion4: You can specify from whom you want me to delete the messages with `{{prefix}}clear @Usuario`.

premium.ayudaDes:
The system works by means of keys, when you obtain it you are assigned a key with your username that cannot be exchanged by another person, therefore you must exchange it on the server you want and it only lasts 1 month until you get another one in this way you can use the benefits on one server per month.
In the case of partners, they will have a key only associated with their server for an unlimited time or until their partner is removed and therefore the benefits.
premium.ayudaField1:
√ó Advanced IpLogger filter - Blocks the triple of directions (+800) and links than the basic filter.
√ó Image filter - Blocks and deletes NSFW images (porn or gore) that are sent out of NSFW channels.
√ó Auto Forceban - Bans or unbans users that are added or removed from the forceban automatically.
premium.ayudaField2:
`redeem` Lets you redeem your key in the server you are.
`info` It shows the current information of your benefits (time you have left, etc).
`safergen` Generates your key if you are Safer II in our server.
premium.ayudaFooter: Remember that you need to write the prefix when using a command and that you don't need to put <>.
premium.errorNoKey: You don't have a key to open my heart :(.
premium.errorNoServidor: You can only use this command in our server, `https://discordsafe.com/discord`.
premium.errorPartner: You are partner and can't redeem your premium in another server.
premium.errorYaKey: You already have a key, you can't have two, I'm not ready for a polyamorous relationship yet.
premium.infoFooter: Remember that only you can use your key, sharing it would do nothing.
premium.noArgsDes: It is a premium benefit for Partners, Safers and donors.
premium.noArgsField1:
√ó Advanced Iplogger Filter (+800 blocked).
√ó Filter images (NSFW or gore out of nsfw channels).
√ó Auto Forceban every time a user is added or removed.
√ó More coming soon.
premium.noArgsField2:
√ó Obtaining Safer II, [learn more on our server](https://discordsafe.com/discord).
√ó Being a partner in [our server](https://discordsafe.com/discord).
√ó [Patreon](https://patreon.com/DiscordSafe).
premium.noArgsFooter: To obtain more information use d.premium help
